metadata.name: A Magical element by the Gods!
metadata.description:
This is a piece generate with AI that I prompted the generator to produce for me. 

I entered the prompt, magic element and then presented it with an image of a chalice, golden, one that a priest would use. And before you, It created the magical element by the gods.

It's always interesting to see how the AI will react to my prompts, Beautiful!   More to come....
